0.SqlCommand:
EXEC sp_set_session_context @key = 'all_access', @value = 1;

WITH TimePeriod([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable]) AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT 
        rd.year, 
        rd.month, 
        DATENAME(MONTH, DATEADD(MONTH, rd.month - 1, CAST('2008-01-01' AS datetime))) AS month_name,
        DATENAME(MONTH, DATEADD(MONTH, rd.month - 1, CAST('2008-01-01' AS datetime))) + ' ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR(4), rd.year),
        CONVERT(VARCHAR(4), rd.year) + '-' + RIGHT('0' + CONVERT(VARCHAR(2), rd.month), 2)
    FROM 
        rpt.DimDate rd
    WHERE 
        rd.year >= 2024 
        AND rd.date <= GETDATE()
),
Providers(id, name) AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT 
        ra.createdByUserFk, 
        ra.createdByUserName 
    FROM   
        rpt.Assessment ra
),
TimePeriod_Providers([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable], [ProviderId], [ProviderName]) AS (
    SELECT * 
    FROM TimePeriod 
    CROSS JOIN Providers 
    WHERE [Year] <= YEAR(GETDATE())
),
ML_ASST_COUNTS([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable], [ProviderId], [ProviderName], [Molecu-lite Imaging Count]) AS (
    SELECT 
        tp_p.[Year], 
        tp_p.MonthNumber, 
        tp_p.[Month], 
        tp_p.MonthYear, 
        tp_p.MonthYearSortable, 
        tp_p.[ProviderId], 
        tp_p.ProviderName, 
        COUNT(DISTINCT ml_asst_id) 
    FROM 
        TimePeriod_Providers tp_p
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (
        SELECT 
            asst.id ml_asst_id,  
            asst.createdByUserFk AS createdByUserFk, 
            asst.date AS ml_asst_date 
        FROM 
            rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion atv    
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Assessment asst ON atv.id = asst.assessmentTypeVersionFk  
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Note nt ON nt.assessmentFk = asst.id  
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.AttributeType atype ON atype.id = nt.attributeTypeFk  
        WHERE  
            atv.assessmentTypeId = '9A4B2FEA-78A8-A1F7-8761-224C0516A846' -- Diagnostic Procedure  
            AND atype.attributeTypeKey = '31970433-6959-A829-AE4F-224C051BB324' -- Instrument/Equipment  
            AND nt.value LIKE 'Bacterial Fluorescence Imaging' -- Molecu-lite Imaging
    ) ml_asst ON tp_p.[ProviderId] = ml_asst.createdByUserFk 
    AND tp_p.Year = YEAR(ml_asst_date) 
    AND tp_p.MonthNumber = MONTH(ml_asst_date)
    GROUP BY 
        tp_p.[Year], tp_p.MonthNumber, tp_p.[Month], tp_p.MonthYear, tp_p.MonthYearSortable, tp_p.[ProviderId], tp_p.ProviderName
),
NI_ASST_COUNTS([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable], [ProviderId], [ProviderName], [Near Infrared Spectroscopy Count]) AS (
    SELECT 
        tp_p.[Year], 
        tp_p.MonthNumber, 
        tp_p.[Month], 
        tp_p.MonthYear, 
        tp_p.MonthYearSortable, 
        tp_p.[ProviderId], 
        tp_p.ProviderName, 
        COUNT(DISTINCT ni_asst_id) 
    FROM 
        TimePeriod_Providers tp_p
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (
        SELECT 
            asst.id ni_asst_id,  
            asst.createdByUserFk AS createdByUserFk, 
            asst.date AS ni_asst_date 
        FROM 
            rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion atv    
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Assessment asst ON atv.id = asst.assessmentTypeVersionFk  
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Note nt ON nt.assessmentFk = asst.id  
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.AttributeType atype ON atype.id = nt.attributeTypeFk  
        WHERE  
            atv.assessmentTypeId = '9A4B2FEA-78A8-A1F7-8761-224C0516A846' -- Diagnostic Procedure  
            AND atype.attributeTypeKey = '31970433-6959-A829-AE4F-224C051BB324' -- Instrument/Equipment  
            AND nt.value LIKE 'Near Infrared Spectroscopy' -- Near Infrared Spectroscopy Imaging
    ) ni_asst ON tp_p.[ProviderId] = ni_asst.createdByUserFk 
    AND tp_p.Year = YEAR(ni_asst_date) 
    AND tp_p.MonthNumber = MONTH(ni_asst_date)
    GROUP BY 
        tp_p.[Year], tp_p.MonthNumber, tp_p.[Month], tp_p.MonthYear, tp_p.MonthYearSortable, tp_p.[ProviderId], tp_p.ProviderName
),
DBD_ASST_COUNTS([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable], [ProviderId], [ProviderName], [Debridement Count]) AS (
    SELECT 
        tp_p.[Year], 
        tp_p.MonthNumber, 
        tp_p.[Month], 
        tp_p.MonthYear, 
        tp_p.MonthYearSortable, 
        tp_p.[ProviderId], 
        tp_p.ProviderName, 
        COUNT(DISTINCT dbd_asst_id) 
    FROM 
        TimePeriod_Providers tp_p
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (
        SELECT 
            asst.id dbd_asst_id,  
            asst.createdByUserFk AS createdByUserFk, 
            asst.date AS dbd_asst_date 
        FROM 
            rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion atv    
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Assessment asst ON atv.id = asst.assessmentTypeVersionFk  
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Note nt ON nt.assessmentFk = asst.id  
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.AttributeType atype ON atype.id = nt.attributeTypeFk  
        WHERE  
            atv.assessmentTypeId = '096cd3b9-7999-aa42-abb3-223104d6e743' -- Wound Procedure  
            AND atype.attributeTypeKey = '8E6177F2-08B0-A55F-888A-22BB045D7401' -- Overall goal of procedure  
            AND (nt.value LIKE 'Reduce bacterial colonization.' 
                 OR nt.value LIKE 'Remove devitalized or infected tissue, particulate matter, or foreign tissues that may impede wound healing.' 
                 OR nt.value LIKE 'Sharp removal of hypergranulation tissue.')
    ) dbd_asst ON tp_p.[ProviderId] = dbd_asst.createdByUserFk 
    AND tp_p.Year = YEAR(dbd_asst_date) 
    AND tp_p.MonthNumber = MONTH(dbd_asst_date)
    GROUP BY 
        tp_p.[Year], tp_p.MonthNumber, tp_p.[Month], tp_p.MonthYear, tp_p.MonthYearSortable, tp_p.[ProviderId], tp_p.ProviderName
),
WOUND_ASST_COUNTS([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable], [ProviderId], [ProviderName], [Wound Assessment Count]) AS (
    SELECT 
        tp_p.[Year], 
        tp_p.MonthNumber, 
        tp_p.[Month], 
        tp_p.MonthYear, 
        tp_p.MonthYearSortable, 
        tp_p.[ProviderId], 
        tp_p.ProviderName, 
        COUNT(DISTINCT wnd_asst_id) 
    FROM 
        TimePeriod_Providers tp_p
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (
        SELECT 
            asst.id wnd_asst_id,  
            asst.createdByUserFk AS createdByUserFk, 
            asst.date AS wnd_asst_date 
        FROM 
            rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion atv    
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Assessment asst ON atv.id = asst.assessmentTypeVersionFk  
        WHERE  
            atv.assessmentTypeId = '952A706D-AA8B-ADBD-4E57-EF6BA5B20B65' -- Wound assessment
    ) wound_asst ON tp_p.[ProviderId] = wound_asst.createdByUserFk 
    AND tp_p.Year = YEAR(wnd_asst_date) 
    AND tp_p.MonthNumber = MONTH(wnd_asst_date)
    GROUP BY 
        tp_p.[Year], tp_p.MonthNumber, tp_p.[Month], tp_p.MonthYear, tp_p.MonthYearSortable, tp_p.[ProviderId], tp_p.ProviderName
),
VISIT_ASST_COUNTS([Year], [MonthNumber], [Month], [MonthYear], [MonthYearSortable], [ProviderId], [ProviderName], [Visit Details Count]) AS (
    SELECT 
        tp_p.[Year], 
        tp_p.MonthNumber, 
        tp_p.[Month], 
        tp_p.MonthYear, 
        tp_p.MonthYearSortable, 
        tp_p.[ProviderId], 
        tp_p.ProviderName, 
        COUNT(DISTINCT visit_asst_id) 
    FROM 
        TimePeriod_Providers tp_p
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (
        SELECT 
            asst.id visit_asst_id,  
            asst.createdByUserFk AS createdByUserFk, 
            asst.date AS visit_asst_date 
        FROM 
            rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion atv    
        INNER JOIN 
            rpt.Assessment asst ON atv.id = asst.assessmentTypeVersionFk  
        WHERE  
            atv.assessmentTypeId = 'A4664A75-1E9A-4537-A663-401954F5593D' -- Visit details
    ) visit_asst ON tp_p.[ProviderId] = visit_asst.createdByUserFk 
    AND tp_p.Year = YEAR(visit_asst_date) 
    AND tp_p.MonthNumber = MONTH(visit_asst_date)
    GROUP BY 
        tp_p.[Year], tp_p.MonthNumber, tp_p.[Month], tp_p.MonthYear, tp_p.MonthYearSortable, tp_p.[ProviderId], tp_p.ProviderName
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
    mlc.MonthYear, 
    mlc.MonthYearSortable AS 'Year-Month', 
    mlc.ProviderId, 
    (SELECT TOP 1 ProviderName
     FROM ML_ASST_COUNTS 
     WHERE MonthYear = mlc.MonthYear 
       AND MonthYearSortable = mlc.MonthYearSortable 
       AND ProviderId = mlc.ProviderId) AS ProviderName, 
    mlc.[Molecu-lite Imaging Count] AS 'Moleculight Imaging', 
    nic.[Near Infrared Spectroscopy Count] AS 'Near Infrared Spectroscopy', 
    dbdc.[Debridement Count] AS 'Debridement', 
    wac.[Wound Assessment Count] AS 'Wound Assessment', 
    vac.[Visit Details Count] AS 'Visit Details'
FROM 
    ML_ASST_COUNTS mlc 
LEFT JOIN 
    NI_ASST_COUNTS nic ON nic.MonthYear = mlc.MonthYear 
    AND nic.MonthYearSortable = mlc.MonthYearSortable 
    AND nic.ProviderId = mlc.ProviderId 
LEFT JOIN 
    DBD_ASST_COUNTS dbdc ON dbdc.MonthYear = mlc.MonthYear 
    AND dbdc.MonthYearSortable = mlc.MonthYearSortable 
    AND dbdc.ProviderId = mlc.ProviderId 
LEFT JOIN 
    WOUND_ASST_COUNTS wac ON wac.MonthYear = mlc.MonthYear 
    AND wac.MonthYearSortable = mlc.MonthYearSortable 
    AND wac.ProviderId = mlc.ProviderId 
LEFT JOIN 
    VISIT_ASST_COUNTS vac ON vac.MonthYear = mlc.MonthYear 
    AND vac.MonthYearSortable = mlc.MonthYearSortable 
    AND vac.ProviderId = mlc.ProviderId
ORDER BY 
    mlc.MonthYearSortable, mlc.ProviderId;
